								var done = PlayerProgress.IsChallengeCompleted( challenge.Id );
								<div onclick=@(() => { PlayClickSound(); _selectedMapId = popupMapId; _selectedTier = popupTier; _selectedChallengeId = challenge.Id; _challengePopupOpen = false; })
								     style="cursor: pointer; border: 2px solid @(selected ? "#c8a800" : "#3a2510"); background-color: @(selected ? "#241b08" : "#140d06"); border-radius: 8px; padding: 8px 10px;">
									<div style="display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between; gap: 8px;">
										<div style="font-size: 14px; color: @(selected ? "#f5c518" : "#ddd"); font-weight: bold;">@challenge.Name</div>
										<div style="font-size: 11px; color: #f5c518;">@($"{challenge.RunCoinMultiplier:F2}x run coins")</div>
									</div>
									<div style="font-size: 11px; color: #a08050; margin-top: 3px;">@challenge.Description</div>
									<div style="font-size: 11px; color: #8a6a40; margin-top: 4px;">@($"Goal: {ChallengeGoalLabel( challenge.Goal )} • Permanent: +{challenge.PermanentBonusPercent:F0}%")</div>
									@if ( done )
									{
										<div style="font-size: 11px; color: #7ee27e; margin-top: 4px;">✓ Completed</div>
									}
								</div>
							}
						}
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		}
	}

	@* ══════════════════════════════════════════════════
	    UNLOCKS PANEL
	   ══════════════════════════════════════════════════ *@
	else if ( _view == MenuView.Unlocks )
	{
		<div style="position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; right: 0; bottom: 0; background-color: rgba(0,0,0,0.55);" onmousedown=@StopPropagation></div>
		<div class="list-panel" onmousedown=@StopPropagation>
			<div class="list-panel-header">
				<div class="list-panel-header-inner">
					<div style="font-size: 32px; font-weight: 900; color: #f5c518; letter-spacing: 4px; text-shadow: 2px 2px 0 #000;">UNLOCKS</div>
					<div style="margin-left: auto; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px; background-color: #120c04; border: 2px solid #6a4a1a; padding: 6px 14px; border-radius: 6px;">
						<img src="ui/coin.png" style="width: 42px; height: 42px; flex-shrink: 0;" />
						<span style="font-size: 16px; color: #f5c518; font-weight: bold; font-family: Minecraft;">@PlayerProgress.Data.Coins</span>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
			<div class="list-panel-tabs">
				<div class="list-panel-tabs-inner">
					@foreach ( UnlockCategory cat in System.Enum.GetValues( typeof(UnlockCategory) ) )
					{
						var catTotal = UnlockDefinition.ForCategory( cat ).Count;
						var catOwned = UnlockDefinition.ForCategory( cat ).FindAll( u => PlayerProgress.IsUnlocked( u.Id ) ).Count;
						var isActive = cat == _unlockTab;
						<div class="tab @(isActive ? "tab-active" : "")" onclick=@(() => { PlayClickSound(); _unlockTab = cat; })>
							@cat.ToString()
							<span style="font-size: 11px; color: @(isActive ? "#f5c518" : "#a08050"); margin-left: 4px;">@catOwned/@catTotal</span>
						</div>
					}
				</div>
			</div>
			<div class="list-panel-scroll list-panel-scroll-inner" onmousedown=@StopPropagation>
					@foreach ( var item in unlockItems )
					{
						var isOwned      = PlayerProgress.IsUnlocked( item.Id );
						var meetsPrereq  = PlayerProgress.MeetsPrerequisite( item.Id );
						var canAfford    = PlayerProgress.Data.Coins >= item.CoinCost;
						var prereqQuest  = item.PrerequisiteQuestId != null ? QuestDefinition.All.Find( q => q.Id == item.PrerequisiteQuestId ) : null;
						var charName     = ( _unlockTab == UnlockCategory.Characters && item.Id.StartsWith( "char_" ) ) ? (char.ToUpper( item.Id[5] ) + item.Id[6..]) : null;
						var weaponIcon   = ( _unlockTab == UnlockCategory.Weapons && item.Id.StartsWith( "weapon_" ) ) ? WeaponIconPath( item.Id ) : null;
						var tomeIcon     = ( _unlockTab == UnlockCategory.Tomes && item.Id.StartsWith( "tome_" ) ) ? TomeIconPath( item.Id ) : null;
						var itemIcon     = ( _unlockTab == UnlockCategory.Items && item.Id.StartsWith( "item_" ) ) ? ItemIconPath( item.Id ) : null;
						var cardIconBg   = isOwned ? "#2a1e08" : charName != null ? CharColor( charName ) : "#1a1008";
						var cardBorder   = isOwned ? "#c8a800" : meetsPrereq ? "#6a4a1a" : "#3a2510";
						var cardIcon     = charName != null ? "" : UnlockCategoryIcon( _unlockTab );
						var cardClass    = isOwned ? "unlock-owned" : !meetsPrereq ? "unlock-locked" : canAfford ? "unlock-affordable" : "unlock-locked";

						<div class="unlock-card @cardClass">
							<div class="unlock-card-top">
								<div class="unlock-card-icon" style="background-color: @cardIconBg; border: 2px solid @cardBorder; border-radius: 8px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; font-size: 24px; opacity: @(meetsPrereq || isOwned ? "1" : "0.4");">
									@if ( charName != null )
									{
										<img src="@CharIconPath( charName )" style="width: 48px; height: 48px; image-rendering: pixelated;" />
									}
									else if ( weaponIcon != null )
									{
										var isEmberTrail = item.Id == "weapon_embertrail";
										@if ( isEmberTrail )
										{
											<div style="width: 50px; height: 50px; background-image: url('@weaponIcon'); background-size: 25% 100%; background-position: 37.5% center; background-repeat: no-repeat; image-rendering: pixelated;"></div>
										}
										else
										{
											<div style="width: 48px; height: 48px; background-image: url('@weaponIcon'); background-size: 33.33% 100%; background-position: center; background-repeat: no-repeat; image-rendering: pixelated;"></div>
										}
									}
									else if ( tomeIcon != null )
									{
										<div style="width: 48px; height: 48px; background-image: url('@tomeIcon'); background-size: 33.33% 100%; background-position: center; background-repeat: no-repeat; image-rendering: pixelated;"></div>
									}
									else if ( itemIcon != null )
									{
										<img src="@itemIcon" style="width: 48px; height: 48px; image-rendering: pixelated;" />
									}
									else
									{
										<text>@cardIcon</text>
									}
								</div>
								<div class="unlock-card-content">
									<div class="unlock-card-name" style="color: @(isOwned ? "#f5c518" : (meetsPrereq ? "#ffffff" : "#cccccc"));">@item.Name</div>
									<div class="unlock-card-desc" style="color: @(meetsPrereq || isOwned ? "#e8d8b0" : "#b89870");">@item.Description</div>
									@if ( !isOwned && !meetsPrereq && prereqQuest != null )
									{
										<div class="unlock-card-prereq" style="color: #d4aa60;"><img src="ui/locked.png" style="width: 10px; height: 10px; flex-shrink: 0; image-rendering: pixelated;" /><span style="white-space: nowrap;">Complete:</span> @prereqQuest.Description</div>
									}
								</div>
							</div>
							<div class="unlock-card-action">
								@if ( item.IsFree || isOwned )
								{
									<div style="display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 6px;">
										<div style="font-size: 18px; color: #f5c518;">✓</div>
										<div style="font-size: 12px; color: #f5c518; letter-spacing: 1px; font-weight: bold;">OWNED</div>
									</div>
								}
								else if ( !meetsPrereq )
								{
									<img src="ui/locked.png" style="width: 32px; height: 32px; image-rendering: pixelated; opacity: 0.9;" />
								}
								else
								{
									<div class="buy-btn @(canAfford ? "buy-btn-ok" : "buy-btn-no")" onclick=@(() => { PlayClickSound(); UnlockTryBuy( item.Id ); })>
										<img src="ui/coin.png" style="width: 24px; height: 24px; flex-shrink: 0;" />
										<span class="buy-btn-cost" style="font-size: 14px; font-weight: bold; color: @(canAfford ? "#f5c518" : "#a08050");">@item.CoinCost</span>
									</div>
								}
							</div>
						</div>
					}
			</div>
			@if ( _unlockFeedback != null )
			{
				<div style="flex-shrink: 0; text-align: center; padding: 10px 20px; font-size: 14px; color: @(_unlockFeedbackErr ? "#f55" : "#f5c518"); background-color: #120c04; border-top: 2px solid #6a4a1a; font-family: Minecraft;">@_unlockFeedback</div>
			}
			<div class="list-panel-footer">
				<div class="list-panel-footer-inner">
					<div class="back-btn" onclick=@(() => { PlayClickSound(); _view = MenuView.Main; })>← BACK</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	}

	@* ══════════════════════════════════════════════════
	    QUESTS PANEL
	   ══════════════════════════════════════════════════ *@
	else if ( _view == MenuView.Quests )
	{
		<div style="position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; right: 0; bottom: 0; background-color: rgba(0,0,0,0.55);" onmousedown=@StopPropagation></div>
		<div class="list-panel" onmousedown=@StopPropagation>
			<div class="list-panel-header">
				<div class="list-panel-header-inner">
					<div>
						<div style="font-size: 32px; font-weight: 900; color: #f5c518; letter-spacing: 4px; text-shadow: 2px 2px 0 #000;">QUESTS</div>
						<div style="font-size: 12px; color: #a08050; letter-spacing: 2px; margin-top: 3px;">@completedQuests / @totalQuests COMPLETED</div>
					</div>
					<div style="margin-left: auto; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px; background-color: #120c04; border: 2px solid #6a4a1a; padding: 6px 14px; border-radius: 6px;">
						<img src="ui/coin.png" style="width: 42px; height: 42px; flex-shrink: 0;" />
						<span style="font-size: 16px; color: #f5c518; font-weight: bold; font-family: Minecraft;">@PlayerProgress.Data.Coins</span>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
			<div class="list-panel-tabs">
				<div class="list-panel-tabs-inner">
					@foreach ( var filter in QuestFilters )
					{
						var isActive = filter == _questFilter;
						<div class="tab @(isActive ? "tab-active" : "")" onclick=@(() => { PlayClickSound(); _questFilter = filter; })>@(filter)</div>
					}
				</div>
			</div>
			<div class="list-panel-scroll list-panel-scroll-inner" onmousedown=@StopPropagation>
					@foreach ( var quest in filteredQuests )
					{
						var qprog        = PlayerProgress.GetQuestProgress( quest.Id );
						var qclaimed     = PlayerProgress.IsQuestClaimed( quest.Id );
						var qclaim       = PlayerProgress.CanClaimQuest( quest.Id );
						var qpct         = qclaimed ? 100 : (int)System.Math.Min( 100, (float)qprog / quest.Target * 100 );
						var questCharName = quest.GoalType == QuestGoalType.KillsAsCharacter ? (UnlockDefinition.All.Find( u => u.Id == quest.CharacterId )?.Name ?? "") : "";

						<div class="quest-row @(qclaimed ? "quest-done" : (qclaim ? "quest-claimable" : ""))">
							<div class="quest-row-top">
								@if ( quest.GoalType == QuestGoalType.KillsAsCharacter )
								{
									<div class="quest-row-icon" style="background-color: @CharColor(questCharName); border: 2px solid @(qclaimed ? "#c8a800" : (qclaim ? "#c8a800" : "#6a4a1a")); border-radius: 6px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;">
										<img src="@CharIconPath(questCharName)" style="width: 40px; height: 40px; image-rendering: pixelated;" />
									</div>
								}
								else if ( QuestIconImg( quest.GoalType ) is {} qstImgPath )
								{
									<div class="quest-row-icon" style="background-color: @(qclaimed ? "#2a1e08" : (qclaim ? "#2a1e00" : "#1a1008")); border: 2px solid @(qclaimed ? "#c8a800" : (qclaim ? "#c8a800" : "#6a4a1a")); border-radius: 6px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;">
										<img src="@qstImgPath" style="width: 40px; height: 40px;" />
									</div>
								}
								else
								{
									<div class="quest-row-icon" style="background-color: @(qclaimed ? "#2a1e08" : (qclaim ? "#2a1e00" : "#1a1008")); border: 2px solid @(qclaimed ? "#c8a800" : (qclaim ? "#c8a800" : "#6a4a1a")); border-radius: 6px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; font-size: 26px;">
										@QuestIcon( quest.GoalType )
									</div>
								}
								<div class="quest-row-content">
									<div style="font-size: 15px; font-weight: bold; color: @(qclaimed ? "#f5c518" : "#eee");">@quest.Description</div>
									<div style="background-color: #120c04; height: 12px; width: 100%; border: 1px solid #5a3a10; border-radius: 4px; margin-top: 8px;">
										<div style="background-color: @(qclaimed ? "#c8a800" : (qclaim ? "#e8b800" : "#8a5a20")); height: 100%; width: @qpct%; border-radius: 4px;"></div>
									</div>
									<div style="font-size: 12px; color: #a08050; margin-top: 6px; white-space: nowrap;">
										@(qclaimed ? $"{quest.Target:N0} / {quest.Target:N0}" : $"{System.Math.Min(qprog,quest.Target):N0} / {quest.Target:N0}")
									</div>
								</div>
							</div>
							<div class="quest-row-action">
								<div style="display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 6px;">
									<img src="ui/coin.png" style="width: 24px; height: 24px;" />
									<span style="font-size: 14px; font-weight: bold; color: #f5c518;">@quest.CoinReward</span>
								</div>
								@if ( qclaimed )   { <div style="display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 6px;"><div style="font-size: 18px; color: #f5c518;">✓</div><div style="font-size: 12px; color: #f5c518; font-weight: bold;">DONE</div></div> }
								else if ( qclaim ) { <div class="claim-btn" onclick=@(() => { PlayClickSound(); QuestClaim( quest.Id ); })>CLAIM</div> }
								else               { <div style="font-size: 11px; color: #6a4a1a; letter-spacing: 1px;">LOCKED</div> }
							</div>
						</div>
					}
			</div>
			@if ( _questFeedback != null )
			{
				<div style="flex-shrink: 0; text-align: center; padding: 10px 20px; font-size: 14px; color: #f5c518; background-color: #120c04; border-top: 2px solid #6a4a1a; font-family: Minecraft;">@_questFeedback</div>
			}
			<div class="list-panel-footer">
				<div class="list-panel-footer-inner">
					<div class="back-btn" onclick=@(() => { PlayClickSound(); _view = MenuView.Main; })>← BACK</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	}
	}

</root>


@code
{
	static SoundEvent UiClick = new( "sounds/ui_click.mp3" );
	static SoundEvent QuestClaimSound = new( "sounds/quest_claim.mp3" );

	void PlayClickSound()
	{
		try { Sound.Play( UiClick ); } catch { }
	}

	enum MenuView { Main, CharacterSelect, MapSelect, Unlocks, Quests }
	MenuView _view = MenuView.Main;

	string _selectedMapId = "dark_forest";
	int    _selectedTier  = 1;
	string _selectedChallengeId = null;
	bool _challengePopupOpen = false;
	string _challengePopupMapId = "dark_forest";
	int _challengePopupTier = 1;
	bool _mapDetailsOpen = false;

	UnlockCategory _unlockTab          = UnlockCategory.Characters;
	string         _unlockFeedback     = null;
	bool           _unlockFeedbackErr;
	float          _unlockFeedbackTimer;

	static readonly string[] QuestFilters = { "All", "Kills", "Survival", "Level", "Character", "Runs", "Weapon", "Tome", "Deaths", "No Damage", "Chests", "Projectiles" };
	string _questFilter   = "All";
	string _questFeedback = null;
	float  _questFeedbackTimer;

	bool _questNotify => QuestDefinition.All.Exists( q => PlayerProgress.CanClaimQuest( q.Id ) );

	// ── Leaderboard ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
	class LbEntry { public int Rank; public string DisplayName; public long Value; public ulong SteamId; }

	List<LbEntry> _lbKills    = new();
	List<LbEntry> _lbSurvival = new();
	List<LbEntry> _lbRuns     = new();
	bool _lbLoading = true;
	bool _lbError   = false;
	float _lbRefreshTimer   = 0f;
	float _lbRefreshCooldown = 0f;
	const float LbRefreshInterval = 60f;

	async Task RefreshLeaderboardAsync()
	{
		_lbLoading = true; _lbError = false;
		try
		{
			var bKills    = Sandbox.Services.Leaderboards.GetFromStat( "roguegames.ultimatesurvivors", "total_kills" );
			var bSurvival = Sandbox.Services.Leaderboards.GetFromStat( "roguegames.ultimatesurvivors", "best_survival" );
			var bRuns     = Sandbox.Services.Leaderboards.GetFromStat( "roguegames.ultimatesurvivors", "runs_played" );
			bKills.MaxEntries = bSurvival.MaxEntries = bRuns.MaxEntries = 11; // fetch 11 so filtering dev accounts still leaves 10 to display
			await Task.WhenAll( bKills.Refresh(), bSurvival.Refresh(), bRuns.Refresh() );
			_lbKills    = ProcessBoard( bKills );
			_lbSurvival = ProcessBoard( bSurvival );
			_lbRuns     = ProcessBoard( bRuns );
		}
		catch { _lbError = true; _lbKills.Clear(); _lbSurvival.Clear(); _lbRuns.Clear(); }
		finally { _lbLoading = false; }
	}

	List<LbEntry> ProcessBoard( Sandbox.Services.Leaderboards.Board2 board )
	{
		return board.Entries
			.Select( e => new LbEntry { Rank = (int)e.Rank, DisplayName = e.DisplayName ?? "???", Value = (long)e.Value, SteamId = (ulong)e.SteamId } )
			.Where( e => !e.DisplayName.Contains( "BoldTrooper", System.StringComparison.OrdinalIgnoreCase ) )
			.Take( 10 )
			.Select( ( e, i ) => new LbEntry { Rank = i + 1, DisplayName = e.DisplayName, Value = e.Value, SteamId = e.SteamId } )
			.ToList();
	}

	string LbFormatKills( long value ) => value >= 1000 ? $"{value / 1000.0:F1}K" : value.ToString();

	// ── Chat ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
	struct ChatEntry { public string Name; public string Text; public string ColorHex; }

	bool _chatOpen = false;
	bool _chatSubscribed = false;
	List<ChatEntry> _chatMessages = new();
	const int MaxMenuChatMessages = 120;
	static readonly TimeSpan MenuChatHistoryWindow = TimeSpan.FromMinutes( 15 );
	int _onlineCount = 0;
	float _onlineRefreshTimer = 0f;
	const float OnlineRefreshInterval = 1f;

	void OnChatPanelClick( PanelEvent e )
	{
		PlayClickSound();
		if ( !_chatOpen ) _chatOpen = true;
	}

	void OnMenuChatSubmit( PanelEvent e )
	{
		if ( e.Target is not TextEntry te ) return;
		var msg = te.Text?.Trim() ?? "";
		_chatOpen = false;
		if ( string.IsNullOrEmpty( msg ) ) return;

		var name = Connection.Local?.DisplayName ?? Connection.Local?.Name ?? "Player";

		// Show message immediately (optimistic), then broadcast.
		AppendMenuChatEntry( new ChatEntry { Name = name, Text = msg, ColorHex = "#ffffff" } );
		StateHasChanged();

		var chat = ChatComponent.Instance;
		if ( chat != null )
		{
			chat.CurrentInput = msg;
			chat.Submit();
		}
	}

	void OnChatMessageAdded()
	{
		var chat = ChatComponent.Instance;
		if ( chat == null || chat.Messages.Count == 0 ) return;
		var latest = chat.Messages[^1];
		// Avoid duplicating the optimistic message we already added locally.
		if ( _chatMessages.Count > 0 &&
		     _chatMessages[^1].Name == latest.PlayerName &&
		     _chatMessages[^1].Text == latest.Text )
			return;
		_chatMessages.Add( new ChatEntry
		{
			Name     = latest.PlayerName,
			Text     = latest.Text,
			ColorHex = MenuChatColor( latest.NameColor )
		} );
		TrimMenuChatBuffer();
	}

	void AppendMenuChatEntry( ChatEntry entry )
	{
		_chatMessages.Add( entry );
		TrimMenuChatBuffer();
	}

	void TrimMenuChatBuffer()
	{
		if ( _chatMessages.Count <= MaxMenuChatMessages ) return;
		_chatMessages.RemoveRange( 0, _chatMessages.Count - MaxMenuChatMessages );
	}

	void RefreshMenuChatFromHistory()
	{
		var chat = ChatComponent.Instance;
		if ( chat == null ) return;

		_chatMessages = chat.GetRecentMessages( MenuChatHistoryWindow )
			.Select( msg => new ChatEntry
			{
				Name = msg.PlayerName,
				Text = msg.Text,
				ColorHex = MenuChatColor( msg.NameColor )
			} )
			.ToList();

		TrimMenuChatBuffer();
		StateHasChanged();
	}

	void StopPropagation( PanelEvent e ) => e.StopPropagation();

	string MenuChatColor( Color c )
	{
		int r = (int)(c.r * 255);
		int g = (int)(c.g * 255);
		int b = (int)(c.b * 255);
		return $"#{r:X2}{g:X2}{b:X2}";
	}

	protected override void OnStart()
	{
		Panel.Style.PointerEvents = PointerEvents.All;
		_lbRefreshTimer = LbRefreshInterval;
		_onlineCount = Connection.All.Count;
		_onlineRefreshTimer = OnlineRefreshInterval;
		RefreshMenuChatFromHistory();
	}

	protected override void OnEnabled()
	{
		// Always return to the main page (not map/character select) when the menu re-appears after a run.
		_view = MenuView.Main;
		_lbRefreshTimer = 0f;
		_onlineCount = Connection.All.Count;
		_onlineRefreshTimer = 0f;
		_ = RefreshLeaderboardAsync();
		RefreshMenuChatFromHistory();
	}

	protected override void OnDestroy()
	{
		if ( _chatSubscribed && ChatComponent.Instance != null )
			ChatComponent.Instance.OnMessageAdded -= OnChatMessageAdded;
	}

	protected override void OnUpdate()
	{
		if ( _unlockFeedback != null )
		{
			_unlockFeedbackTimer -= Time.Delta;
			if ( _unlockFeedbackTimer <= 0f ) _unlockFeedback = null;
		}
		if ( _questFeedback != null )
		{
			_questFeedbackTimer -= Time.Delta;
			if ( _questFeedbackTimer <= 0f ) _questFeedback = null;
		}

		// Subscribe to ChatComponent once it becomes available.
		if ( ChatComponent.Instance != null && !_chatSubscribed )
		{
			ChatComponent.Instance.OnMessageAdded += OnChatMessageAdded;
			_chatSubscribed = true;
			RefreshMenuChatFromHistory();
		}

		// Leaderboard refresh cooldown (manual button).
		if ( _lbRefreshCooldown > 0f )
			_lbRefreshCooldown -= Time.Delta;

		// Keep "ONLINE" indicator fresh while idling in menu.
		_onlineRefreshTimer -= Time.Delta;
		if ( _onlineRefreshTimer <= 0f )
		{
			_onlineRefreshTimer = OnlineRefreshInterval;
			int latestOnline = Connection.All.Count;
			if ( latestOnline != _onlineCount )
			{
				_onlineCount = latestOnline;
				StateHasChanged();
			}
		}

		// Periodic auto-refresh every 60 s while on the main view.
		if ( _view == MenuView.Main && !_lbLoading )
		{
			_lbRefreshTimer -= Time.Delta;
			if ( _lbRefreshTimer <= 0f )
			{
				_lbRefreshTimer = LbRefreshInterval;
				_ = RefreshLeaderboardAsync();
			}
		}
	}

	// ── Character Selection ───────────────────────────────────────────────
	string _selectedCharName = null;

	void OnMuteClicked()
	{
		PlayClickSound();
		MusicManager.Instance?.ToggleMute();
	}

